long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhance your Google search experience with the Display Results Number extension. Instantly know how many search results are available for your query without scrolling to the bottom. Key features:

Quick Insight: Displays the total number of search results right at the top of the Google search page, so you can instantly assess the relevance and scope of your search.
Seamless Integration: Blends naturally into the Google search page, preserving the look and feel you're accustomed to.
Time Saver: No need to scroll or guess the search results volume, saving you time and effort.
Customizable Display: Adjust the display location and style according to your preference for a personalized experience.
Lightweight & Fast: Consumes minimal resources, ensuring a smooth browsing experience
